prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous flat 2D vector illustration for a birthday card, botanical style. In the center, a comically grumpy cartoon sloth hangs upside down from a lush, leafy green monstera branch that frames the top of the card. The sloth is wearing a tiny, brightly colored party hat that is slightly askew on its head. One of its claws is loosely holding the string of a single, slightly deflated-looking helium balloon that floats limply beside it. The sloth has a hilariously unimpressed, deadpan expression on its face, as if reluctantly participating in the celebration. The background is a clean, solid cream color. The entire scene is enclosed within a delicate, hand-drawn circular border made of intertwined ferns and tropical leaves. In the safe center area, below the sloth, the text "happy birthday, or whatever" is written in a beautiful, elegant, and readable handwritten cursive script in a dark forest green color. The overall aesthetic is minimalist, witty, and artistically rendered with clean lines and a soft, natural color palette.
